						               													<description>Creatures: The Card Game, later released as Creature Clash!, is a creative, strategic card game that blends friendly competition with a good laugh!  It is intended for 2 to 6 players, ages 8 and up.  The game is comprised of 96 playing cards consisting of either a &amp;lsquo;FRONT&amp;rsquo;, &amp;lsquo;MIDDLE&amp;rsquo;, or &amp;lsquo;BACK&amp;rsquo; portion of 32 particular animals.  Each animal is illustrated across the three cards, and includes a fun fact about that animal and a corresponding &amp;lsquo;strength&amp;rsquo; value ranging from 1-10 (e.g. a mosquito is strength-1, and a grizzly bear is strength-10).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Gameplay occurs as players mix and match &amp;lsquo;FRONT&amp;rsquo;, &amp;lsquo;MIDDLE&amp;rsquo;, and &amp;lsquo;BACK&amp;rsquo; cards in their hand to create entirely new creatures, and stage attacks against the creatures in other players&amp;rsquo; hands.  For example, the &amp;lsquo;FRONT&amp;rsquo; of Octopus (4), the &amp;lsquo;MIDDLE&amp;rsquo; of Hippopotamus (7), and the &amp;lsquo;BACK&amp;rsquo; of Armadillo (1) combine to create OC-POTA-DILLO (12)!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
